{"tid":258951,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次砌機求指點,with list求修正","createTime":"2017-05-26T14:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T11:37:53.000Z","uid":44133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6196ab03e92af62859ae58bb085f8d4020f36703","tid":258951,"uid":44133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:06:38.000Z","msg":"都做左好幾日功課追左POST,原本拎悠2個LIST想汁小小但係D PARTS好似都已經OPTIMISE哂.想巴打指點幾個問題同埋而家list咁樣你會唔會有咩修改建議?budget6-7k,其實而家已經到頂..我search左jumbo同中央田既網上報價,都差不多,想問下到場全set咁買會唔會有得打拆?<br />\n我見有巴打話jumbo係水貨黎?<br />\n<br />\n1.主板同樣用350B呢張晶片 唔同牌子GIGABYTE,ASUS,MSI,ASOCK等等 應該點選擇?<br />\n<br />\n2.同上但係FOR 顯示卡<br />\n<br />\n3.其實我唔係用好多位,如果SSD想縮小小有冇得諗?<br />\n<br />\n4.原本悠2個LIST用Skaroon VG4個機箱,想問下我如果轉Skaroon S25會唔會唔夠位?<br />\n<br />\n5. 個機箱頂位可以放多兩個風扇想請問下如果放應該抽風定入風?(原本個箱前2後1)<br />\n<br />\n6. rx 580我見輸出有3個\t<br />\nDual-link DVI-D *1<br />\nHDMI *1 <br />\nDisplay Port *3<br />\n想問下有冇話邊一隻最好?<br />\n<br />\n7.如果砌機我買齊上面d零件係咪就可以定係還要再買d連接線材?ps我有hdmi線.keyboard同mouse"},{"pid":"cf1ebc3ac76a3238b67f9ad41d25daab60441a75","tid":258951,"uid":65092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:29:16.000Z","msg":"你咁問 有點擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3fba83bfa843f8be8bcddfa2262012d6c3f358","tid":258951,"uid":44133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/yQCh0E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FyQCh0E.png&h=6ce3d4bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b515f5edf8a8be9ba1991320a0a0d4769191636","tid":258951,"uid":44133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咁問 有點擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以先想問清楚...求巴打指點下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6385ed6fd76442fbe89a566d2fef6b2d650fa61","tid":258951,"uid":65092,"like":0